        <briefdescription>
<para>Convert CF32 spectrum to F32 dB. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>out(k) = 20*log10(max(|in(k)|, lin_floor)) + offset_db</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
