</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>out</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>F32 output, length <computeroutput>n</computeroutput> (caller-allocated). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>lin_floor</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Amplitude floor before log10 (e.g. 1e-12f). </para>
